Privacy Policy for Adv.DocExporter

Last Updated: April 12, 2026


DATA COLLECTION

Adv.DocExporter does not collect, transmit, or store any telemetry,
analytics, or personal data.

All processing occurs locally within your YouTrack instance.


EXTERNAL SERVICES

The app does not contact any external services. All export operations (XLSX,
DOCX generation) are performed entirely within the YouTrack app runtime.

No external services are contacted.


DATA PROCESSING

  - The app reads Knowledge Base article and issue content via YouTrack's
    internal API to generate export files.
  - Generated files are delivered directly to the user's browser as downloads.
  - No article content, user data, or credentials are logged or transmitted to
    third parties.


CONTACT

For privacy-related questions, contact: apps@mag1.cc
